Subbarao Says Intervention ‘Brings Unexpected Consequences’

-- B y   D r e w   B e n s o n
-- 
2011-09-26T17:06:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/subbarao-says-intervention-brings-unexpected-consequences-.html
Reserve Bank of India Governor
Duvvuri Subbarao said today that “intervention in forex markets
brings unexpected consequences.” Speaking at an event in  New
York , he said “the fear now is that monetary policy is becoming
hostage to fiscal compulsions.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Drew Benson in Buenos Aires at 
 abenson9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kevin Costelloe at 
 kcostelloe@bloomberg.net  